\fs24 If you need to use tables or figures in your essay, you can label them using the following tags, replacing \'93KEYWORD\'94 with a unique word that identifies your table or figure.\
\
!fig(KEYWORD)\
!table(KEYWORD)\
\
These tags will be replaced with numbers in the compiled document, with the numbering stream for figures being separate from the numbering stream for tables.\
\
You can refer to such tags as follows:\
